latestPosts.caption:
Creating a look for someone so close to your heart for the biggest day of their life culminates into one single thing for me - goosebumps through and through! 

I’ve gone back and forth so many times but here we are, I’m finally sharing Himani’s wedding looks starting with the Mehendi Mela where her look was reminiscent of what the event was 💙💜💙

My beautiful baby girl @himani_shaarma #BridesByShradhaLuthra 

This @toraniofficial lehenga was an easy choice – the moment I saw it, I knew it perfectly matched her personality and vibe. For the jewelry, we opted for stunning heritage pieces from @ajewelsbyanmol and finished the look with soft glam for the face.

Snippets from the magical day that this was 💗

latestPosts.caption:
I’ve always told my brides that, somehow, the universe has a way of aligning everything beautifully—everything falls into place just as it should! Over the years, working behind the scenes, I’ve been grateful to witness this magic unfold countless times.

On day three of Ashna and Rishi’s wedding in breathtaking Montreux, Switzerland, it started to rain, and all we had were prayers. But we carried on, got Ashna ready, and, in perfect timing, the sun broke through just in time for her bridal entry, giving her the dream wedding she envisioned against the Swiss Alps.

This is why I’ll forever believe in ‘wedding day magic.’ 

Ashna and Rishi, may your life together be as magical as your wedding day. Thank you for making me a part of your beautiful celebration 🤍

#BridesByShradhaLuthra
